{"parentUuid":"93619faa-ecdd-4787-84a1-0927338dd442","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/bbuchsbaum/code/brainflow2","sessionId":"91173f36-8530-4394-bc18-855b1cf43c77","version":"1.0.43","message":{"id":"msg_01DvfcZm8kJZkeaCgy8Y6wjE","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"claude-opus-4-20250514","content":[{"type":"text","text":"To update Claude Code, you can use one of these methods:\n\n**1. Auto-update (default):**\nClaude Code automatically checks for updates and installs them by default.\n\n**2. Manual update:**\n```bash\nnpm update -g @anthropic/claude-code\n```\n\n**3. Check current version:**\n```bash\nclaude --version\n```\n\n**4. Disable auto-updates:**\nIf you want to control updates manually, you can disable auto-updates in your settings by adding:\n```json\n{\n  \"autoUpdate\": false\n}\n```\n\nThe auto-updater runs in the background and will notify you when updates are available."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":4,"cache_creation_input_tokens":8560,"cache_read_input_tokens":10273,"output_tokens":148,"service_tier":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CQo3tReyUyb5W62rTriR9","type":"assistant","uuid":"6b62121f-81b1-4c04-b909-d64e72fcf32e","timestamp":"2025-07-05T02:03:48.248Z"}
